init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself living a good life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself taking your family to a nice restaurant and enjoying a good meal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The police are there within minutes, but there is no trace of her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You can change your next life if you want, but it will be the last time, at least for this round."
